{"tid":456432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(香港電影票房) 杜汶澤《空手道》不敵王晶《追龍》","createTime":"2017-11-03T03:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T04:00:49.000Z","uid":134071,"like":15,"dislike":157,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"726762fbcf19d262707193fd901bea90ec37aead","tid":456432,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T03:10:07.000Z","msg":"杜汶澤《空手道》首日票房：3,500人次　（每場平均人次：25）<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/58274\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F58274&d=pyKiqRhuC3oNCkX1YkdmvjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=4db7dac4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/58274</a><br />\n<br />\n王晶《追龍》首日票房：12,500人次　（每場平均人次：60）<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/57709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F57709&d=pyKiqRhuC3oNCkX1YkdmvjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=733b40c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/57709</a><br />\n<br />\n好多人成日鬧大陸合拍片. 但就算單以香港票房黎計, 《追龍》票房都打低哂《樹大招風》, 《踏血尋梅》, 《一念無明》, 《點五步》, 《29+1》等誠意本土電影, 所以真係抵王晶牙擦."},{"pid":"948543c58519a6bd246b9be5a54c4d869bbc322e","tid":456432,"uid":141461,"like":10,"dislike":14,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T03:11:48.000Z","msg":"堅決維持鍵盤建國"},{"pid":"362a5d104058fe2670865f1e7f861e92e906218e","tid":456432,"uid":53498,"like":88,"dislike":2,"score":86,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T03:12:25.000Z","msg":"計返成本呢？淨計片酬,劉華加宇宙最強,都貴過杜汶澤十倍"},{"pid":"6dbd3815b7a04ab0f5404efb8c0d3bfb89eb14fa","tid":456432,"uid":141820,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T03:13:01.000Z","msg":"世人只看演員陣容"},{"pid":"4b2d94c88fb7b5dcd30760270e6974afd9c9eb12","tid":456432,"uid":156363,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"一個地方有點樣既觀眾咪有點樣既票房囉，證明本土真係唔會係主流。"},{"pid":"459848f10842946453af3a975a3cb8143d3be20f","tid":456432,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,