faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n觀眾對好多港產片無信心... 除左王晶片  <br />\n<br />\n所以《追龍》香港票房可以打低哂《樹大招風》, 《踏血尋梅》, 《一念無明》, 《點五步》, 《29+1》等誠意本土電影<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 《空手道》香港開畫票房原來仲差過《戰狼II》   (5700人次，每場平均人次65).  香港觀眾寧願看親共大陸片多於香港本土片."},{"pid":"6ac3e07262798f194c1e6399a80789903d3f4788","tid":456432,"uid":109318,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T08:39:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢家啲人睇都睇左鬼佬片 日韓劇先<br />\n邊個睇你港產  中伏太多次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我只可以講 全世界電影都一樣咁多伏<br />\n只不過外國伏片 香港唔會上<br />\n所以咁樣比係唔公平"},{"pid":"cf838b058b344addb1081bcbcc02ec4950a516e3","tid":456432,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T08:41:38.000Z","msg":"有幾出奇?<br />\n追龍卡士 成本大咁多"},{"pid":"12b317d031165d4269be0ae30feb9b747cee4cb4","tid":456432,"uid":48504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T08:42:33.000Z","msg":"香港人有份整死香港樂壇 <br />\n依家又唔支持一下本土電影"},{"pid":"ce0191fdc956af5b6e74e60a6c20f5f228d34148","tid":456432,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T08:43:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢家啲人睇都睇左鬼佬片 日韓劇先<br />\n邊個睇你港產  中伏太多次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我只可以講 全世界電影都一樣咁多伏<br />\n只不過外國伏片 香港唔會上<br />\n所以咁樣比係唔公平</blockquote><br />\n有咩唔公平<br />\n家陣冇限映外國片呢d<br />\n就自然要擺埋黎比<br />\n觀眾買飛個陣你同佢地咁講囉"},{"pid":"45caf372024950821e81d09d59ee7d44ec60554f","tid":456432,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T08:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢家啲人睇都睇左鬼佬片 日韓劇先<br />\n邊個睇你港產  中伏太多次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><